## Tor config for WorldBase darkweb bridge
## SOCKS5 proxy on localhost:9050
SocksPort 9050
## Control port (optional, for circuit rotation)
ControlPort 9051
## Run as background process
RunAsDaemon 0
## Log to file
Log notice file D:/MCP Mods/worldbase/tor/tor.log
## Data directory
DataDirectory D:/MCP Mods/worldbase/tor/data
## GeoIP data
GeoIPFile D:/MCP Mods/worldbase/tor/data/geoip
GeoIPv6File D:/MCP Mods/worldbase/tor/data/geoip6
## Avoid being an exit node (we only need client)
ExitPolicy reject *:*
## No relaying
RelayBandwidthBurst 0
